  "title": "Accounting, Banking & Finance Executive",
  "description": "<p>The Accounting, Banking & Finance Executive is responsible for\nmanaging day-to-day accounting operations and banking activities with a high level of accuracy and accountability. This role suits candidates who are hands-on, independent, and experienced in full-cycle accounting.</p><ul><li>Manage assigned ledgers and accounting cycles</li><li>Prepare journal entries, accruals, and reconciliations</li><li>Execute month-end and year-end closing processes</li><li>Prepare bank payment runs and perform bank reconciliations</li><li>Liaise with banks, auditors, and internal stakeholders</li><li>Prepare management accounts and financial schedules</li><li>Support audits, tax filings, and statutory submissions</li><li>Monitor cash flow and operational finance matters</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Degree in Accounting, Finance, or related field</li><li>3–6 years of relevant experience</li><li>Strong understanding of accounting standards\nand controls</li><li>Proficient in Excel and accounting systems</li><li>Ability to work independently and meet deadlines</li></ul>",
